@startuml data-flow-overview
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam roundCorner 8
skinparam rectangle {
  BorderThickness 2
  FontStyle bold
}

left to right direction

rectangle "**SENSORS**\n<size:9><sensor list></size>" as SENSORS #FEF3C7
rectangle "**ACTUATORS**\n<size:9><actuator list></size>" as ACTUATORS #FED7AA
rectangle "**SPINAL CORD**\n<size:9>firmware Layer-1 + <project>_safety + hardware</size>" as SPINAL #FEE2E2
rectangle "**CEREBELLUM**\n<size:9>EKF · SLAM · Nav2 · BT.CPP</size>" as CEREBELLUM #DBEAFE
rectangle "**CORTEX**\n<size:9><project>_mission · (P2) <project>_perception · (P3) <project>_llm</size>" as CORTEX #E0E7FF
rectangle "**INFRASTRUCTURE**\n<size:9>micro_ros_agent · foxglove_bridge · operator · storage</size>" as INFRA #F3F4F6

' Sensing flow (data IN)
SENSORS    --> SPINAL     : "<size:10>raw I/O</size>"
SPINAL     --> CEREBELLUM : "<size:10>micro-ROS topics\n/imu · /odom · /scan · /sonar · /tof</size>"
CEREBELLUM --> CORTEX     : "<size:10>fused state\n/odom · /map · /mission/status</size>"

' Control flow (commands OUT)
CORTEX     --> CEREBELLUM : "<size:10>mission goals\n/navigate_to_pose</size>"
CEREBELLUM --> SPINAL     : "<size:10>/cmd_vel\n<size:9>safety-filtered</size></size>"
SPINAL     --> ACTUATORS  : "<size:10>PWM · I²C · GPIO</size>"

' Safety override (red = hard)
SPINAL <-[#DC2626,bold]-> CEREBELLUM : "<size:10>/emergency_stop ⇆ /safety/override</size>"

' Infra cross-cuts
INFRA  <--> CORTEX     : "<size:10>operator commands · status</size>"
INFRA  <-- CEREBELLUM  : "<size:10>visualisation</size>"
INFRA  <-- SPINAL      : "<size:10>diagnostics · audit</size>"

note bottom of SPINAL
**Two physical homes:** firmware (atomic safety,
< 200 ms) + PC-side `<project>_safety` package (policy).
**Hard thresholds** never overridable; **soft thresholds**
audit-logged via /safety/override.
end note

note bottom of INFRA
Carries every cross-layer message —
micro_ros_agent (UDP :8888), foxglove_bridge (WS :8765),
audit logs / saved maps / rosbag2 on disk.
end note

@enduml
